title: Yen near 160, a record Nikkei 225, higher yields: What experts expect after Sanae Takaichi's landslide victory
summary_full: Takaichi led the ruling Liberal Democratic Party to a supermajority in the Lower House, securing 316 seats in Japan's largest election win since World War Two.
summary_public: Takaichi led the ruling Liberal Democratic Party to a supermajority in the Lower House, securing 316 seats in Japan's largest election win since World War Two.
